title: Sissyaki Women's Long Sleeve Boho Floral Maxi Dress Smocked Beach Flowy Dress
description: This dress is made of high quality polyester, lightweight and breathable, partial lined, comfy hand touch, wonderful material for women.
Flowy and feminine, this ultra-flattering long dress is designed in a beautiful vintage-inspired floral print.with a smocked waist detail for added definition.
A flowy bohemian long dress featuring encased elasticised lantern sleeves, a long flatter skirt. The plunge v neckline highlights the decolletage.
Smocking and summer go together like fresh air and sunshine. It's no wonder we're wearing these cute, sweet, elegant styles all season long.
Wear this casual piece over your favorite high heels or sandals, enjoy your cool summer days.Suitable for casual, daily, date, office, business, vacation, beach, etc.
